        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### \u20ac 3.800,00 to clear\n\n\u2705 **Follow your plan (+\u20ac 305,00/mo) \u2192 debt-free in ~13 months.**\n\n\u274c **Keep overspending (\u20ac 7.387,00/mo like now) \u2192 never** \u2014 you go backwards.\n\n\ud83d\udc49 The whole game = keep spending at **\u20ac 5.314,00**, not \u20ac 7.387,00. Online shopping is the lever."
